        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for sending Wallace’s book [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">13313</hi>]</p> 
            <p>and for writing to Hooker about FdeAF’s plants. Has written to Hooker to tell him of the plants he is sending and discuss the subject of the cypress trunks.</p>
            <p>Thanks CD for his detailed instructions for suggested experiments.</p>
        </abstract>
